        Hillenburg is survived by his wife of 20 years, Karen Hillenburg, and son Clay. The SpongeBob SquarePants series has seen more than 200 episodes broadcast and has spawned two successful animated films. The cartoon has also been made into a Broadway musical - with original songs by David Bowie, John Legend and Cyndi Lauper - which won a Tony Award earlier this year.
                
                
                
                
                
            
            
